## Collections.Collectible class

Simple implementation of [ICollectible](./ts-utils.collections.icollectible.md) which does not allow the index to be changed once set.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare class Collectible<TKEY extends string = string, TINDEX extends number = number> implements ICollectible<TKEY, TINDEX> 
```
